ActIndian Act
SubjectSettlement agreement between Canada and the Bigstone Cree Nation
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada to execute 1) the Bigstone Cree Nation Specific Claims Settlement Agreement between Canada and the Bigstone Cree Nation, 2) the Treaty Land Agreement between Canada and the Peerless Trout First Nation and 3) the Canada/Alberta Settlement Agreement between Canada and Her Majesty in Right of the Province of Alberta.
